{"title":"冬（二首）","authors":["李钧"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李钧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪纷纷扬扬的雪片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似翩翩飞舞的银蝶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树枝抖落雪屑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象柳絮轻轻飘逸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆雪人的孩子们多么欢悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕冷的只有屋檐下的麻雀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活是一本本春天的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬，只是一张洁白的扉页。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！是冬雪轻吻着茫茫田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是春鸟正跳上你的眉睫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪地上挺着翡翠的宝塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野里绿着的只有她。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季都不挂奇葩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是落雪时披一点银花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚假的装饰她根本不爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤一股轻风把雪片抖下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！雪地上挺着翡翠的宝塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象你，象我，也象他。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}